snippet.title: Amber Heard SLAMMED For "Racist" Tweet
snippet.description:
Amber Heard attempted to tweet about immigration, but it EPICLY backfired on Twitter. Brett, Grace, Jason and Daron break down the tweet and the tweets that followed once people started to respond. Let us know if you think her tweet was racist in the comments below. 

********************************

Pop Trigger is your unfiltered talk show about real life. Everyday we talk about entertainment, the internet, culture, and important social issues. We don't just scratch the surface, we talk about the real truths behind the seemingly ordinary.
